OL,3,CChildren as young as 12 can now join
OL,4,Cwar effort in Iran
OL,6,FIran's security forces have invited
OL,7,Fchildren as young as 12 to participate
OL,8,Fin war-related activity, Iranian media
OL,9,Fhas reported.
OL,11,FA branch of the Islamic Revolutionary
OL,12,FGuard Corps (IRGC) has announced an
OL,13,Finitiative called 'For Iran', which
OL,14,Fwill recruit volunteers as young as 12
OL,15,Fto assist in the war effort, in non-
OL,16,Farmed combat roles.
OL,18,FThe comments were broadcast as part of
OL,19,Fstate media coverage of the war effort.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
