OL,3,CChildren as young as 12 can now join
OL,4,Cwar effort in Iran
OL,6,FUnder international law, children are
OL,7,Fnot allowed to be recruited or used in
OL,8,Fhostilities, helping to protect them
OL,9,Ffrom exploitation.
OL,11,FIranian state media have said the
OL,12,Fscheme aims to drive public support
OL,13,Fand utilise the skills of Iranian
OL,14,Fcitizens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
