OL,3,CChildren as young as 12 can now join
OL,4,Cwar effort in Iran
OL,6,FSpeaking to Iranian state-affiliated
OL,7,Fnews agency Defa Press, Rahim Nedaali,
OL,8,Fthe Cultural and Artistic Deputy of
OL,9,Fthe Tehran-based Mohammad Rasoulollah
OL,10,FCorps, said: "Given the strong public
OL,11,Fresponse, we have created a framework
OL,12,Fin which all interested individuals
OL,13,Fcan contribute to the defence of the
OL,14,Fcountry according to their expertise
OL,15,Fand abilities."
OL,17,FReports suggest that the campaign
OL,18,Fcovers several areas, such as:
OL,26,@rD@NOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
