OL,3,CChildren as young as 12 can now join
OL,4,Cwar effort in Iran
OL,6,FNedaali added that those interested
OL,7,Fcan register at bases for the Basij
OL,8,FResistance Force, a voluntary
OL,9,Fparamilitary organisation under the
OL,10,FIRGC, or at a pop-up registration
OL,11,Fbooth in the main square.
OL,13,FIn a state broadcast, Nedaali said:
OL,14,F"Given that the age of those coming
OL,15,Fforward has dropped and they are
OL,16,Fasking to take part, we lowered the
OL,17,Fminimum age to 12," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@SO]
