OL,3,CChildren as young as 12 can now join
OL,4,Cwar effort in Iran
OL,6,FUnder the Convention on the Rights of
OL,7,Fthe Child, a core UN human rights
OL,8,Fagreement, "States Parties shall take
OL,9,Fall feasible measures to ensure that
OL,10,Fpersons who have not attained the age
OL,11,Fof 15 years do not take a direct part
OL,12,Fin hostilities."
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
