OL,3,CChildren as young as 12 can now join
OL,4,Cwar effort in Iran
OL,6,FIran has drawn criticism from human
OL,7,Frights groups such as Amnesty
OL,8,FInternational in relation to children
OL,9,Fbeing detained and facing the death
OL,10,Fpenalty.
OL,12,FThis is not the first time Iran has
OL,13,Finvited children to participate in a
OL,14,Fwar effort. During the Iran-Iraq war,
OL,15,Fthousands of Iranian children were
OL,16,Fsent to the front lines.
OL,18,FMany children volunteered after seeing
OL,19,Fstate propaganda, as well as being
OL,20,Finfluenced by religious ideology.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
